&lt;h1 id="enjoy-your-work"&gt;Enjoy your work&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No profit grows where is no pleasure ta&amp;rsquo;en;&lt;br&gt;
In brief, sir, study what you most affect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;— William Shakespeare, &lt;em&gt;The Taming of the Shrew&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To really get anywhere in mathematics requires &lt;strong&gt;hard work&lt;/strong&gt;. If you don&amp;rsquo;t enjoy what you are doing, and do not derive satisfaction from your contributions, it will be difficult to put in the sustained amounts of energy required to succeed in the long term.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>